import { combineReducers } from "redux"
import wellsReducer from "./wellsReducer"
import selectWellFromReduxStoreReducer from "./selectWellFromReduxStoreReducer"
import postPlansToJSONdb from "./postPlansToJSONdb"
import saveNewWellToReduxStoreReducer from "./selectWellFromReduxStoreReducer"

export default combineReducers({
  wells: wellsReducer,
  activeWell: selectWellFromReduxStoreReducer,
  plansSuccessfullyPosted: postPlansToJSONdb, 
  currentWell: saveNewWellToReduxStoreReducer
})
